<div id="review_49201251" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/49201251" />
    <a title="Julie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1213607-julie"><img alt="Julie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1612145096p2/1213607.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/49201251?book_show_action=true">Mar 13, 2009</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Julie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Julie" href="/user/show/1213607-julie">Julie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>


          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">historical fiction buffs, fans of adventure/thrillers</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1213607-julie?shelf=east-central-europe">east-central-europe</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1213607-julie?shelf=european-setting-multiple-countries">european-setting-multiple-countries</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1213607-julie?shelf=past-and-present-setting">past-and-present-setting</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1213607-julie?shelf=read-2009">read-2009</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1213607-julie?shelf=best-of-2009">best-of-2009</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer49201251" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16088156860197555479">I adored this novel! It contained all the elements of my favorite contemporary fiction: impeccable historical research, geographic locales that are as strong as the characters, characters who are multi-dimensional &amp; believable, a plot that weaves multiple threads and themes in good pace and with precision. With this, Brooks moves into my favorite authors column. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


